name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent, v. William NEAL, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 8th day of November, 2007, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is granted. The Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus/Mandamus/Prohibition and/or Extraordinary Relief and the Application for Relief are denied.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
